{"tid":2011601,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼滅之刃第二部即將展開","createTime":"2020-05-11T06:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T17:40:24.000Z","uid":32645,"like":3,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ca505cc6da01dcd5e0a9b97b12a5c1580fb93e05","tid":2011601,"uid":32645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"食用兒童歷盡艱辛，與***訂立契約後啟程前往人類世界，但潛伏的陰謀亦偷偷尾隨著......<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，因開啟了斑紋而即將死亡的炭次郎，看到了從窗口飄到床邊的藍色彼岸花，嗅到了不妙的氣息，著禰豆子急喚昔日的鬼殺隊員前來。但在善逸、伊之助等人到來之前已經長眠......<br />\n<br />\n都市中出現神秘的連續殺人事件，主角煉獄是一位善良的少年，他一家在一夜之間死光，只有妹妹倖免卻得了狂化怪病，被稱之為「鬼」。為了將變成鬼的妹妹變回人類、並為死去的家人報仇雪恨，他加入了專門狩獵惡鬼的組織「鬼殺隊」，新一代故事即將展開！"},{"pid":"83bc3d843c67ee5babe5cec6df3ee8609025cef1","tid":2011601,"uid":12186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:18:31.000Z","msg":"又係阿妹變鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d242afaf6652c24b2f77c4f93c2a1db44b4ce2e","tid":2011601,"uid":24270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:22:54.000Z","msg":"比啲source 黎好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a4520666a78954a63176a8fa4e25da26ca1d0f","tid":2011601,"uid":192075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:25:10.000Z","msg":"堅唔堅呀？"},{"pid":"4a9853b56ef1f51f7de29e278414d090682b2839","tid":2011601,"uid":218494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:31:24.000Z","msg":"兩個唔同漫畫黎喎屌你"},{"pid":"94e5daa737d5974c078c9382505ea35104c20f7d","tid":2011601,"uid":1900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"睇到食用兒童都知fake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89986025edc0a8221aefb115e4861a8b27200d3d","tid":2011601,"uid":32645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94e5daa737d5974c078c9382505ea35104c20f7d","tid":2011601,"uid":1900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:40:51.000Z","m